{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"11":{"eng-name":"The Rites of Hajj (Kitab Al-Manasik Wa'l-Hajj)","ara-name":"كتاب المناسك"}},"section_detail":{"11":{"hadithnumber_first":1721,"hadithnumber_last":2045,"arabicnumber_first":1721,"arabicnumber_last":2045}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1944,"arabicnumber":1944,"text":"حدثنا محمد بن كثير، حدثنا سفيان، حدثني ابو الزبير، عن جابر، قال افاض رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم وعليه السكينة وامرهم ان يرموا بمثل حصى الخذف واوضع في وادي محسر","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":11,"hadith":224},"chapter":{"id":66,"ara-name":"باب التَّعْجِيلِ مِنْ جَمْعٍ","eng-name":"Leaving Early From Jam' (Al-Muzdalifah)","isFirstHadith":false}}]}